§ Definition ⦉
¶ ⦊
  ‖ For any $a ∈ 𝗥^n$ and $α ∈ 𝗥$, the sets
    ◇ ⦊
      ‖ \Set{x ∈ 𝗥^n}{a^\tp x ≤ α}, \quad \Set{x ∈ 𝗥^n}{a^\tp x
        ≥ α} ⦉
    ⦉
    are called ❬closed halfspaces❭ and the sets
    ◇ ⦊
      ‖ \Set{x ∈ 𝗥^n}{a^\tp x < α}, \quad \Set{x ∈ 𝗥^n}{a^\tp x
        > α} ⦉
    ⦉
    are called ❬open halfspaces❭. ⦉
⦉

